Subject: [PATCH 2/14] octeon: import the Cavium executive runtime

The octeon executive runtime the driver builds on, under
arch/mips/cavium-octeon/executive. It has the BGX MAC, the PKI, PKO3, FPA3
and SSO bookkeeping, the QLM lane init, and the cvmx helper files.

Signed-off-by: Amaan Qureshi <git@amaanq.com>
